<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Vircosa | Luxury Fragrances</title>

    <!-- Bootstrap CSS -->
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <!-- Font Awesome -->
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <!-- Google Fonts (Playfair Display + Montserrat) -->
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@400;700&family=Montserrat:wght@300;400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <!-- Custom CSS -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../stylesheets/navbar-styles.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../stylesheets/footer-styles.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../stylesheets/main-styles.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../stylesheets/cta-section-styles.css">

    <style>
        /* ===== Hero Section ===== */
        .hero-section {
            background: linear-gradient(rgba(42, 33, 24, 0.4), rgba(42, 33, 24, 0.4)),
                url('../images/hero-img.avif') no-repeat center center;
            background-size: cover;
            color: white;
            padding: 180px 0 150px;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
        }

        .hero-title {
            font-size: 4rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-shadow: 1px 1px 3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        }

        .hero-subtitle {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            opacity: 0.9;
            font-weight: 300;
        }

        .btn-hero {
            background-color: var(--primary-color);
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 35px;
            border-radius: 30px;
            font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            border: none;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .btn-hero:hover {
            background-color: var(--secondary-color);
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        /* ===== Products Section ===== */
        .products-section {
            padding: 100px 0;
            background-color: white;
        }

        .section-title {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 60px;
        }

        .section-title h2 {
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--secondary-color);
            position: relative;
            display: inline-block;
            padding-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .section-title h2:after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            width: 80px;
            height: 2px;
            background-color: var(--primary-color);
            bottom: 0;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
        }

        .product-card {
            background-color: var(--light-color);
            border-radius: 10px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
            transition: all 0.4s ease;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .product-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .product-img {
            height: 500px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .product-img img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
            transition: transform 0.5s ease;
        }

        .product-card:hover .product-img img {
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }

        .product-body {
            padding: 25px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .product-title {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            color: var(--secondary-color);
        }

        .product-desc {
            color: #666;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }

        .product-price {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--primary-color);
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .btn-product {
            background-color: transparent;
            border: 1px solid var(--primary-color);
            color: var(--primary-color);
            padding: 8px 25px;
            border-radius: 30px;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .btn-product:hover {
            background-color: var(--primary-color);
            color: white;
        }

        /* ===== About Section ===== */
        .about-section {
            padding: 100px 0;
            background-color: var(--light-color);
        }

        .about-img {
            border-radius: 10px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 15px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .about-img img {
            width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            transition: transform 0.5s ease;
        }

        .about-img:hover img {
            transform: scale(1.03);
        }

        .about-content h2 {
            color: var(--secondary-color);
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }

        .about-content p {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #555;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }

        /* ===== Responsive Adjustments ===== */
        @media (max-width: 992px) {
            .hero-title {
                font-size: 3rem;
            }

            .hero-subtitle {
                font-size: 1.2rem;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .navbar-brand {
                font-size: 1.5rem;
            }

            .hero-section {
                padding: 120px 0 100px;
            }

            .product-img {
                height: 300px;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 576px) {
            .hero-title {
                font-size: 2.2rem;
            }

            .section-title h2 {
                font-size: 1.8rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <%- include('partials/navbar') %>

        <!-- Hero Section -->
        <section class="hero-section">
            <div class="container">
                <h1 class="hero-title">Elegance in Every Drop</h1>
                <p class="hero-subtitle">Discover the art of fragrance with Vircosa</p>
                <a href="/products" class="btn btn-hero">Explore Scents</a>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Products Section -->
        <section class="products-section" id="products">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="section-title">
                    <h2>Our Signature Scents</h2>
                    <p class="text-muted">Crafted with rare ingredients for unforgettable moments</p>
                </div>
                <div class="row">
                    <!-- Product 1: Fleur -->
                    <div class="col-lg-6">
                        <div class="product-card">
                            <div class="product-img">
                                <!-- Replace with your image -->
                                <img src="../images/fleur.png" alt="Fleur Perfume">
                            </div>
                            <div class="product-body">
                                <h3 class="product-title">Fleur</h3>
                                <p class="product-desc">A delicate Floral bouquet with notes of jasmine, rose, and
                                    vanilla.
                                </p>
                                <p class="product-price">$89.00</p>
                                <a href="/products" class="btn btn-product">Discover</a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <!-- Product 2: Whim -->
                    <div class="col-lg-6">
                        <div class="product-card">
                            <div class="product-img">
                                <!-- Replace with your image -->
                                <img src="../images/whim.png" alt="Whim Perfume">
                            </div>
                            <div class="product-body">
                                <h3 class="product-title">Whim</h3>
                                <p class="product-desc">Bold and woody with hints of Amber and Bergamot.</p>
                                <p class="product-price">$95.00</p>
                                <a href="/products" class="btn btn-product">Discover</a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <!-- Product 3: Baran -->
                    <div class="col-lg-6">
                        <div class="product-card">
                            <div class="product-img">
                                <!-- Replace with your image -->
                                <img src="../images/baran.png" alt="Baran Perfume">
                            </div>
                            <div class="product-body">
                                <h3 class="product-title">Baran</h3>
                                <p class="product-desc">Mysterious. Earthy. Elemental power.</p>
                                <p class="product-price">$85.00</p>
                                <a href="/products" class="btn btn-product">Discover</a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Product 4: Zarva -->
                    <div class="col-lg-6">
                        <div class="product-card">
                            <div class="product-img">
                                <!-- Replace with your image -->
                                <img src="../images/Noir.avif" alt="Coco Noir">
                            </div>
                            <div class="product-body">
                                <h3 class="product-title">Noir</h3>
                                <p class="product-desc">Daring. Charismatic. Smooth chaos.</p>
                                <p class="product-price">$79.00</p>
                                <a href="/products" class="btn btn-product">Discover</a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                </div>

            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- About Section -->
        <section class="about-section" id="about">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="row align-items-center">
                    <div class="col-lg-6 mb-4 mb-lg-0">
                        <div class="about-img">
                            <!-- Replace with your image -->
                            <img src="../images/store.jpg" alt="Vircosa Story">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-lg-6">
                        <div class="about-content">
                            <h2>Our Essence</h2>
                            <p>Ever caught a scent that stopped you in your tracks? That’s the magic we bottle at
                                <strong>Vircosa</strong>.
                            </p>
                            <p>We’re not just mixing perfumes—we’re crafting memories. Imagine rare botanicals
                                whispering
                                secrets from Himalayan peaks or Amazonian rainforests, all blended to make you feel
                                something—nostalgia, confidence, maybe even dangerously irresistible.</p>
                            <p>Our signature scents, like <em>Fleur</em> and <em>Whim</em>, aren’t just perfumes—they're
                                stories. Spritz, and you're suddenly the mysterious stranger in someone’s novel.</p>
                            <a href="#" class="btn btn-product mt-3">Dare to Smell Different</a>

                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <%- include('partials/cta-section') %>
        <%- include('partials/newsletter') %>
        <%- include('partials/footer') %>

        <!-- Bootstrap JS (for navbar toggle) -->
        <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
        <!-- Minimal JS for Navbar Scroll Effect -->
        <script>
            window.addEventListener('scroll', function () {
                const navbar = document.querySelector('.navbar');
                if (window.scrollY > 50) {
                    navbar.classList.add('scrolled');
                } else {
                    navbar.classList.remove('scrolled');
                }
            });


        </script>
</body>

</html>